            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong> then pat it dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen paper<strong> </strong>(squeeze as much liquid out as you can)</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p>",
